Selenium Day 8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


ALERTS

	3 cesit alert vardir

		Simple Alert  -> OK

		Prompt Alert -> Input + OK + Cancel

		Confirmation Alert -> OK + Cancel


		driver.switchTo().alert().accept() -> OK
		driver.switchTo().alert().dismiss() -> Cancel
		driver.switchTo().alert().sendKeys() -> Input
		driver.switchTo().alert().getText() -> Alert mesajini verir 


BASIC AUTH

	https://kullaniciadi:sifre@URL

	orn: https://karl:karl123@www.example.com/

IFRAMES

	iFrame html icinde html dokumanidir. iFramedeki elementleri sayfa icerisinde dogrudan locate edemeyiz.
	iFrame icerisine girip locate islemi yapmaliyiz.

	driver.switchTo().frame(int index)
	driver.switchTo().frame(String id or name)
	driver.switchTo().frame(WebElement element)

	driver.switchTo().parentFrame()
	driver.switchTo().defaultContent()


SENDKEYS

	sendKeys methodu ile biz klavyemizde harf olmayan diger fonksiyonel tuslara basabiliriz (ENTER, BACKSPACE, F1, F2, F3 .....)
	
	element.sendKeys(Keys.ENTER)
	element.sendKeys("bir input" + Keys.ENTER)
	
	

